text: Bic Runga (born January 13, 1976) is a singer from New Zealand. She was born in Christchurch. She has sold lots of albums in New Zealand. The names of her albums are: *Drive *Beautiful Collision *Live in Concert (With the Christchurch Symphony) *Birds Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand singers Category:Pop musicians Category:People from Christchurch
title: Bic Runga
